overview: Kennedy is quintessential, young American college jock that you just know has every guy and girl on campus lusting after him. Hot, ripped, hung, athletic — while also smart, charming, humble and fun — this young stud is quite the catch! Colt (Calvin Chambers), Quinn (Quin Quire), Rowan (Gunner Canon), Kellan (Cody Blackford), and Harper all discover here that Kennedy is also quite the incredible fuck in 4 action-packed, hardcore episodes!
title: CF Crush: Kennedy
